snippet.title: STELLAR 7 - DYNAMIX - US GOLD - GAMEPLAY VIDEO C64
snippet.description:
Fast and smooth take on Battlezone (Atari coin op) that I owned right back in the early years of C64 gaming. 

Think it was the first game I ever bought that had a transparent cassette case wooooooooo :o)
